• Use ToDo_List_6 example as baseline for this homework
• Add a button on ToDo List main view (either above the list view or bottom of the list view), name this button "Sync"
	– Alternatively, add a menu item called "Sync" 
• When the above button (or menu icon) is clicked, fire an Intent
	– This Intent shall launch a new Activity to represent "SyncScreen" (chose a layout of your choice to create this view)
	– SyncScreen has one line message about ongoing sync operation
	– SyncScreen has one button called "GoBack"
• When GoBack button is clicked, an Intent is fired which will take user back to main screen of ToDo List
• Add a Yes/No dialog box to confirm removal of an item from ToDo List
	– Optionally, remove the selected item from the ToDo List

